{
  "texts": [
    "See Fig. 3 (Appendix A.2) for an illustration of quality.",
    "The maxim of relevance is given by the following requirements:",
    "(1) The response should directly and relevantly address the recipient's statements in helpful manner.",
    "(2) The response should be relevant to the current topic and not unnaturally shift the conversation to unrelated subjects.",
    "Grice states that relevance requires a participant's \"contribution to be appropriate to the immediate needs\" of the conversation (Grice, 1975)."
  ]
}